lead_paragraph: Tranquillo Barnetta's free kick in the 90th minute kissed off the crossbar and settled into the net and Philadelphia handed Orlando City its first loss of the season, 2-1 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Barnetta's Late Goal Lifts Philadelphia to 2-1 Win
